Package: brrr
Title: Create Benefit-Risk Visualization Plots for Clinical Trials
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Pawel", "Piela", , "pawel.piela@lilly.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides functions for creating benefit-risk visualization plots
    commonly used in clinical trial analysis and regulatory submissions. The 
    package supports forest plots with multiple axes, customizable headers,
    legends, and various visual elements for presenting treatment comparisons.
    Designed for pharmaceutical and biostatistics applications.
Imports:
    grid,
    dplyr (>= 1.0.0),
    R6,
    rlang
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
